    "redesign_intro": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "disabled": true,
      "name": "Redesign intro",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div class=\"page-width page-width--narrow custom-liquid-redesign\" style=\"padding:1rem 0 2rem;\">\n  <h1 class=\"h1\" style=\"margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">Jewelry Redesign &mdash; Bring Your Gems &amp; Jewelry Back to Life</h1>\n  <div class=\"rte\">\n    <p>Some pieces are too meaningful to leave forgotten in a drawer. <strong>Jewelry redesign</strong> gives your old, inherited, or unworn jewelry a second life &mdash; reimagined into something you&rsquo;ll actually wear and treasure. Using your own gems and gold, I redesign rings, necklaces, bracelets, and earrings into timeless, one-of-a-kind heirlooms that carry your story forward.</p>\n    <h2>How Jewelry Redesign Works</h2>\n    <ol>\n      <li><strong>Free virtual consultation.</strong> We talk through your pieces, your story, and what you&rsquo;d love to wear.</li>\n      <li><strong>Send photos of your jewelry or gems.</strong> Share what you have and the vision you have in mind.</li>\n      <li><strong>Custom design.</strong> I design a piece built around your materials and your style.</li>\n      <li><strong>Refining &amp; crafting.</strong> I responsibly refine your old gold and reset your stones into the new design.</li>\n      <li><strong>Your new heirloom.</strong> You receive a piece made to be worn, loved, and passed on.</li>\n    </ol>\n    <h2>What You Can Redesign</h2>\n    <ul>\n      <li><strong>Engagement rings &amp; wedding bands</strong> &mdash; modernize a dated setting or honor a marriage with a fresh design.</li>\n      <li><strong>Inherited &amp; heirloom jewelry</strong> &mdash; turn a grandmother&rsquo;s ring or a mother&rsquo;s necklace into something you&rsquo;ll wear every day.</li>\n      <li><strong>Old or broken gold</strong> &mdash; refine unworn gold and apply its value toward your new piece.</li>\n      <li><strong>Loose or set diamonds &amp; gemstones</strong> &mdash; reset your stones into a setting that suits you now.</li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2>Resetting Your Diamonds &amp; Stones</h2>\n    <p>Already love your stones but not the setting? I reset diamonds and gemstones into entirely new designs &mdash; from a classic solitaire into a sculptural band, or scattered stones gathered into a single statement piece. Your gems stay; the design becomes truly yours.</p>\n    <h2>Use Your Own Gold &amp; Gems</h2>\n    <p>Working with your own materials preserves the sentimental value of the originals, reduces cost, and is far kinder to the environment than buying new. If you have gold or platinum you no longer wear, I refine it and apply its value toward your redesign &mdash; with transparent pricing and work that fits your budget.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin-top:1.5rem;\"><strong>Explore specific services:</strong> <a href=\"/pages/reset-diamond-ring\">Reset a Diamond Ring</a> &middot; <a href=\"/pages/redesign-engagement-ring\">Redesign an Engagement Ring</a> &middot; <a href=\"/pages/heirloom-jewelry-redesign\">Heirloom Jewelry Redesign</a></p></div>\n</div>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 24,
        "padding_bottom": 12
      }
    },
